{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-requestProgress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"title":"progress","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress